{"tid":2373040,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"淫之呼吸！女星神還原鬼滅戀柱　「深溝爆乳」炸飛襯衫釦子","createTime":"2021-01-20T07:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T07:50:57.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4d4b7972a27c7de9795a97b1ab484d051f0eec7a","tid":2373040,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:11:35.000Z","msg":"日本動畫《鬼滅之刃》在全球具有超高人氣，不少COSER也爭相扮演鬼滅當中的角色，日本知名AV女優深田詠美也跟上這波熱潮，先前她才cosplay可愛的禰豆子，這次尺度連跳好幾級，直接扮演在動畫中擁有一雙巨乳的鬼殺隊柱成員「甘露寺蜜璃」，神還原襯衫釦子爆開、露出深溝美胸的戀柱，立刻引發網友熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/20/2992758-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F20%2F2992758-PH.jpg&h=981ffcd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲深田詠美的推特有166萬人追蹤。（合成圖／翻攝自深田えいみ 大喜利AV女優推特）<br />\n<br />\n深田詠美是日本知名的AV女優，時常在推特上分享美照，每次裝扮都讓人相當驚艷，1月15日，她挑戰《鬼滅之刃》中的角色「甘露寺蜜璃」戀柱，只見她神還原戀柱的綠、粉色相間的頭髮，也穿上她專屬的鬼殺隊制服，只見她胸前2、3個釦子整個爆開，露出一雙性感美胸，胸前「深溝」讓人看了快噴鼻血，只差沒露點，尺度直逼18禁，與動畫中害羞又性感的戀柱造型，十分相像。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/20/2992938-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F20%2F2992938-PH.jpg&h=8dc45583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲深田詠美扮演戀柱。（圖／翻攝自深田えいみ 大喜利AV女優推特）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/20/2992751-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F20%2F2992751-PH.jpg&h=e352c256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，她上次也曾COSPLAY過《鬼滅之刃》的角色，扮過禰豆子，也獲得相當大的迴響。這次她挑戰戀柱，深田詠美也留言「戀之呼吸，淫亂柱」，引起網友熱烈討論。戀柱照片一出，目前已有4.5萬名網友按愛心支持，紛紛表示，「我的眼睛只看得到胸部」、「好可愛啊～」、「我已經被迷惑的不要不要了」、「好想變成鬼」、「實在太強了」、「又色又可愛」、「Damn beautiful」、「真的是全集中」、「簡直要升天了啊」、「我覺得妳很適合」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/20/2992752-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F20%2F2992752-PH.jpg&h=7ab0a457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲深田詠美的禰豆子也獲得好評。（圖／翻攝自深田えいみ 大喜利AV女優推特）"},{"pid":"8bb5d153f4b1209d317be086f91218ef7a955bc3","tid":2373040,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:12:44.000Z","msg":"為新AV宣傳鋪路"},{"pid":"054e65b2a615ed3d7e7507a2eb8a4395d16dc27d","tid":2373040,"uid":234509,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:15:03.000Z","msg":"假人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9615b929070ccf2963551bdd494b56c9e7d6b467","tid":2373040,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bb5d153f4b1209d317be086f91218ef7a955bc3","tid":2373040,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:12:44.000Z","msg":"為新AV宣傳鋪路"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:16:38.000Z","msg":"佢d片好仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c3ae7c160df237e5b0da839a30963ff0d3fc65","tid":2373040,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:16:51.000Z","msg":"膠之呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733e27df7d888ef4bf1c3a04fd4e4fd502ffb47f","tid":2373040,"uid":129235,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:19:16.000Z","msg":"On9，我直接去買戀柱d figure 來J 咪得囉，反正大家都係假+膠之嘛!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbbd6326fcdb93f3ae4d3e79043acc13489115b","tid":2373040,"uid":209890,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:20:55.000Z","msg":"諗唔明咩人先會走去J依件膠人<br />\n人膠就算<br />\n波都膠既<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">美谷朱里世界第一</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18a44b5b55320f355d93bb4b714543d6b66ebc3","tid":2373040,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:24:16.000Z","msg":"個